  <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ metadata.title }}</title>
    <meta name="Description" content="{{ renderData.description or description or metadata.description }}">
      {# <link rel="alternate" href="{{ metadata.feed.path | url }}" type="application/atom+xml" title="{{ metadata.title }}"> #}
    {% set css %}
      {% include "style.css" %}
    {% endset %}
    <style>
      {{ css | cssmin | safe }}
    </style>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/typeit@7.0.4/dist/typeit.min.js"></script>

  </head>
  <body>

    <div id="splash-page">
      <div class="script-container">
        <span id="splashText"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="skip-button">
        <a href="#header-container">
          <img src="/assets/skip.png"  />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="header-container">
      <header>
        <div class="title header-item">
          <h1><a href="{{ '/' | url }}">{{ metadata.title }}</a></h1>
        </div>
        <div class="tagline header-item">
          <h2>{{ metadata.tagline }}</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="contact header-item">
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="carousel-container">
        <ul class="carousel-slide">
          <li class="item">
          <img src="/assets/carousel-img/Carouselitem1.jpg" alt="drawing of prisoners sat underneath a tree with a guard standing by">
            <div class="carousel-details">
              <p class="carousel-item-excerpt">By acting now justice can be created worldwide.</p>
              <a class="carousel-item-link" href="/informaljusticecourt/informal-justice-court-in-prison/">To Justice</a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="item">
          <img src="/assets/carousel-img/Carouselitem2.jpg" alt="drawing of the view out of a window overlooking a prison court">
          <div class="carousel-details">
            <p class="carousel-item-excerpt">When the justice system fails, civil society is under attack.</p>
            <a class="carousel-item-link" href="/pretrialproblem/a-serious-problem/">To Jail</a>
          </div>
          </li>
          <li class="item">
          <img src="/assets/carousel-img/Carouselitem3.jpg" alt="drawing of the interior of a guards office">
          <div class="carousel-details">
            <p class="carousel-item-excerpt">With good teamwork we can increase chances of a fair trial.</p>
            <a class="carousel-item-link" href="/partnersinjustice/inmates-protagonists/">To Cast</a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="item">
          <img src="/assets/carousel-img/Carouselitem4.jpg" alt="drawing of seating at a prisons football ground">
          <div class="carousel-details">
            <p class="carousel-item-excerpt">After visits, research and building a network it is time to start the building the Informal Justice Court.</p>
            <a class="carousel-item-link" href="/behindthescenes/latest-news/">To Action</a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="item">
          <img src="/assets/carousel-img/Carouselitem5.jpg" alt="drawing of two prisoners ineracting outside a door">
          <div class="carousel-details">
            <p class="carousel-item-excerpt">A big social impact can be made in Ikoyi Prison by combining social design, art, theatre, academics and the work of NGOâ€™s.</p>
            <a class="carousel-item-link" href="/aboutaardschap/about-us/">To Producer</a>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div id="prevBtn"></div>
        <div id="nextBtn"></div>

      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mobile-home-space">
      <div class="mobile-space-container">
        <p>{{ metadata.tagline }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
      <div>
        {{ content | safe }}
      </div>

      <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/typeit@7.0.4/dist/typeit.min.js"></script>

      <script>
        new TypeIt("#splashText", {
          strings: ["<h1>ACT I</h1>", "<br /><h1>SCENE 1</h1>", "<br />SETTING: IKOYI PRISON, LAGOS, NIGERIA", "<br><br>Mega cities grow fast and so does the pressure on the justice system. Today 15 million people around the world await their trail behind bars. Often for months or even years.", "<br />How can we change this injustice?", " ", " ", " "],
          speed: 50,
          lifeLike: true,
          breakLines: true,
          waitUntilVisible: true,
          afterComplete: function(step, instance) {

            var element = document.getElementById("header-container");
            // smooth scroll to element and align it at the bottom
            element.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'start'});

          }
        }).go();

      </script>
      {% set js %}
        {% include "script.js" %}
      {% endset %}
      <script>
        {{ js | safe }}
      </script>
  </body>
</html>
